    <td class=”h6”>

        <b>E-COMMERSE:</b>

        <br>

        &emsp;&emsp;Any marketing that uses electronicdevices and can be used by marketing specialists to convey promotional messaging and measure its impact through your customer journey. In practice, digital marketing typically refers to marketing campaigns that appear on a computer, phone, tablet, or other device. It can take many forms, including online video, display ads, search engine marketing, paid social ads and social media posts. Digital marketing is often compared to “traditional marketing” such as magazine ads, billboards, and direct mail. Oddly, television is usually lumped in with traditional marketing.

        <td>

            <br>

            <br>

            <br> 

            <br>

            <br>

            <br>

        <img src=”E-commerce.png” height=”500px”>

        </td>

